---
// Asia Interlude — cinematic break between sales and creative sections
---

<section class="asia" id="asia">
  <div class="asia-image-wrapper">
    <img
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1528181304800-259b08848526?w=1920&q=80"
      alt="Aerial view of Southeast Asia coastline"
      class="asia-image"
      loading="lazy"
    />
    <div class="asia-overlay"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="asia-content container reveal">
    <span class="section-label">2024 — 12 Months Across Asia</span>
    <h3 class="asia-headline">
      Some things are worth pressing pause for.
    </h3>
    <p class="asia-text">
      Took a planned career break to travel across Asia with my fiancée, who has a degenerative memory condition. 
      Built a video archive preserving our shared experiences for the future. Returned with a drone pilot's eye, 
      a hard drive full of cinematic footage, and renewed clarity on what comes next.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .asia {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 60vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .asia-image-wrapper {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .asia-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center 40%;
  }

  .asia-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.85) 0%,
      rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.6) 50%,
      rgba(123, 47, 190, 0.15) 100%
    );
  }

  .asia-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 650px;
    padding: 100px 24px;
  }

  .asia-headline {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .asia-text {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-100);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .asia {
      min-height: 50vh;
    }

    .asia-content {
      padding: 80px 24px;
    }
  }
</style>
